nousbot is a simple coffeescript/node.js irc bot meant to do useful things

not ready yet, but hopefully will be soon :)
currently only supports basic functionality
admin commands, screen scraping, events!

be sure to copy the config.coffee.defaults to config.coffee and update the file
ensure your log dir exists and is writeable

requirements are listed in package.json

contributors:
    eggsby
    tanepiper

plugins:
    protomega (stock, tinyurl)
    TheEternalAbyss (urban prototype)
    stenehall (isit)
    joshmanders (weather)

known issues: 
    multiple networks aren't yet supported (but multiple channels is)
    uncaught plugin errors crash entire process
    logging isn't working as expected, logging everything from any channel

